  "notes": [
    "This study demonstrates that ST3Gal1-mediated \u03b12,3-sialylation plays a crucial role in regulating intestinal barrier function and inflammation in ulcerative colitis",
    "The triple-culture model using Caco-2, HT29-MTX-E12, and THP-1 cells provides a valuable in vitro system for studying intestinal barrier function",
    "ST3Gal1 appears to have opposite effects on barrier-protective proteins (MUC2, TFF3, CDX2) versus inflammatory mediators (IL-1\u03b2, IL-6, IL-8, p-STAT3)"
  ]
